2017 I Was Living In This House In 📍Fayetteville, NC When I Went Flat Broke‼️ First My 📱Phone Got Cut Off, Then The Internet, Then The Power & I Had To Pawn My Laptop 💻. No Car, No Money For Food & No Video Shoots. I Left That House & Everything In It & Moved To Atlanta & Slept In A Few Parking Lots & Snuck In A Few Hotels For Free Breakfast 🥞 Until I Met @thetamrasimmons And She Introduced Me To @shadmoss & @iamjusgod & My Entire Life Changed Over Night‼️ Most People Only Post There Wins. But This Was One Of The Darkest Periods Of My Life & I wouldn’t Change A Thing‼️💯🎬 #OTD #motivation #perseverance #grind #fayettevillenc
